[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      181[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### Finding M5 - EMA Outlier Sensitivity
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      182[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+      183[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Severity:** MEDIUM
